  NOTES : Reviewed in "Vegetables your kids will eat," Family Fun Magazine,
  May 1996.  This salad dresses up a plate nicely. Use fresh ingredients and
  toss well to coat the apples and prevent them from browning.
 
</step></directions></recipe></recipeml>
